flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Start of the module assembly process in SAP S/4HANA.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Retrieve cell performance metrics from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: AutoML - Sort cells into modules based on performance metrics.]
  N2 --> N3{PB: Process Builder - Assemble module structures and weld busbars.}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Process Builder - Integrate cooling system components and validate performance.]
  N4 --> N5[PB: Process Builder - Conduct electrical testing and quality gates.]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Process Builder - Optimize module production line cycle times.]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS, improved on-time delivery, and maintained quality across multiple plants, lines, and suppliers.]
  N3 -->|Cell performance metrics are missing ...| B1[Notify operators to manually inspect and sort cells.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Manual intervention to ensure quality.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Cooling system integration fails vali...| B2[Trigger rework process for cooling system components.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Corrective actions taken to meet quality standards.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Electrical testing fails quality gates.| B3[Initiate rework process for electrical components.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Ensures module readiness for final assembly.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]